Edition:
Quote:  Both rock and mud oysters are found all round New Zealand, but only the North Island rock oyster (restricted to the Auckland district) and the Foveaux Strait mud oyster (not confined to

Foveaux Strait) are taken commercially. Our three main oysters are <i>Ostrea hefferdi</i> (southern rock oyster), <i>O. sinuata</i> (mud oyster, ... ), and <i>Saxostrea glomerata</i> (northern rock oyster).
